<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/2 Do you have confidence in yourself or you exist only for others ?]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=714&amp;p=742#p742"><![CDATA[
4/2 Do you have confidence in yourself or you exist only for others ?<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/xzhry83lQRw">https://youtu.be/xzhry83lQRw</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Topics 1 :<br />When we are in a group or in a family, we very much need the approval of our superiors, colleagues, friends, and at the same time we need the approval of our parents. Do you have confidence in yourself or you exist only for others ?<br /><br />Sec1. questions:<br />1. Why We Care About Other People's Approval and Admiration.<br />2. Do you think you are a easy  going person and the person who is easy to make friend with?<br />3. When you want to choose a friend, what are the elements that you concern? <br />4. How to motivate yourself to change your behavior ?<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />Session 1:<br />7:05-7:40 pm <br />Individual Presentation<br />7:40-8:00<br />Group  discussion.<br />Session 2.<br />8:00-8:40 pm<br />Individual <br />8：40-9:00 pm<br />Group  discussion.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Sect.2 <br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://youtu.be/rf1YmgeQrrI">https://youtu.be/rf1YmgeQrrI</a><!-- m --><br />Topics 2 ：<br />In this video, the host introduces a lot of ways to take good care of yourself psychologically and physically. We should understand and learning together.<br /><br />Sect.2. questions:<br />1. How to motivate yourself to change your behavior ?<br />2. Are you content with your situation in the current moment ? if it's not, why ?<br />3.We know that everybody has his own duty for the family, the society  but how about to yourself ?<br />4. Do you  actually knowing how to take care of yourself psychologically and physically？<br />5.Nature can heal our physiology and psychology. Do you often go outdoors?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">dora</a> — Tue Mar 28, 2023 7:59 am</p><hr />
